The diagnostic showed two category levels absent from this dataset (`ecog_ps` has no 3 and `histology` has no large-cell rows), which caused the rank issue. It also showed `pdl1_tps` is encoded as a 0-1 proportion, so I’m correcting the PD-L1 hypotheses and scaling to use 0.50 as the 50-point threshold.
